  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>偏右</span> <span>2026-05-03 13:47</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">重庆</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4cd21315&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fym794MIAO6Ut6IR6l0TaF7mZRe3OMo2GkFkXuwMDZ0ZkiaH3MXh8iaJNZ5JJ8YibISjzPrKdfVGTUVQCoiciaKibmFj29amoicetsdG2TdDUY6aZaQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: black;padding: 0 10px;line-height: 1.6;word-spacing: 0px;letter-spacing: 0px;word-break: break-word;word-wrap: break-word;text-align: left;font-family: Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.33611111111111114\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100037616\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=396daf5d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fym794MIAO6X3ZPJv1BZcHzYx8qqbq5icbXXHfdQkj3RIL6fcr83goovlPrMj37XKjDXA6lg0MaXh3hR987cISedrbJNQnkPLibP9nduuEAqvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">距离 v5 发布已经过去快五年了。五年间，前端世界发生了翻天覆地的变化——React 18/19 带来了并发渲染，antd 从 v4 升级到了 v6，构建工具从 webpack 演进到了 Turbopack，CSS-in-JS 和 Tailwind 成为主流。v6 做了两件事：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">全面拥抱最新技术栈</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，以及</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">清理历史包袱</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"200\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-top: 30px;\" width=\"30\" data-imgfileid=\"100037606\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=29d44b83&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fym794MIAO6Whib0y9cF5XdJs1ialpXlibqfLGpAR68ImOHIDvMBFMG8DOIhM3Ht1RwVP8QOjhGnyUoDAeiaVn2nv01NcsvYXOsZg2H1wkvAlefc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   <h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;color: black;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-top: 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🌟 v6 背后的蚂蚁生态</span></h1>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;color: black;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ant Design V6</span></span><sup style=\"line-height: 0;color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;— 企业级设计系统。Pro v6 全面采用 antd 6，启用 CSS 变量模式（cssVar），支持 Default、Dark、Glass 等多种风格预设，渲染性能显著提升。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ant Design X</span></span><sup style=\"line-height: 0;color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;— AI 界面解决方案，基于 RICH 设计范式将 GUI 与自然语言交互有机融合。Pro v6 内置的 AI 助手页面基于 Ant Design X 构建，开箱即用。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ant Design CLI</span></span><sup style=\"line-height: 0;color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">[3]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;— 官方命令行工具（</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;color: #1e6bb8;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">npx antd</span></code><span leaf=\"\">），查询组件 API、获取示例代码、诊断项目配置一步到位。Pro v6 已内置集成，告别频繁翻文档。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">utoo</span></span><sup style=\"line-height: 0;color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">[4]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;— 基于 Turbopack 的 Rust 构建引擎，提供极速冷启动和毫秒级 HMR。Pro v6 默认使用 utoopack 构建，生产构建提速约 42%。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"200\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-top: 30px;\" width=\"30\" data-imgfileid=\"100037605\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e6d6c18f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fym794MIAO6XnalThRTQbcdNheQ1sXP5FxicCGoB2D9B9I14wSiaDUKTuHFgBBZsLYtp0SxiawbPpibBU5eAReOcpLL8Y2rQbS40JQAB9BaB5VEI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   <h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;color: black;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-top: 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚀 框架升级</span></h1>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;font-weight: bold;color: black;font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 19 + antd 6</span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">v6 基于 React 19 和 antd 6 构建。React 19 的并发特性与 Server Components，antd 6 的设计系统更新与 CSS 变量主题——这些在 v5 中还无法触及的能力，现在开箱即用。</span></p>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;font-weight: bold;color: black;font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Umi Max 4</span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">v5 已在使用 Umi Max，v6 升级到 @umijs/max 4，带来 utoopack 默认构建引擎和更完善的插件体系：</span></p>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto;padding: 16px;color: #abb2bf;background: #282c34;display: -webkit-box;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;border-radius: 0px;font-size: 12px;-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\"><span style=\"color: #e06c75;line-height: 26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">- import { useModel } from 'umi';</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"color: #98c379;line-height: 26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">+ import { useModel, request, useAccess, getLocale, useIntl } from '@umijs/max';</span></span></code></pre>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;font-weight: bold;color: black;font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ProComponents v3</span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">分散的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;color: #1e6bb8;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">@ant-design/pro-table</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;color: #1e6bb8;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">@ant-design/pro-form</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;color: #1e6bb8;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">@ant-design/pro-layout</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;等多个包统一为&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;color: #1e6bb8;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">@ant-design/pro-components</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;v3。一个包解决所有中后台组件需求，版本对齐不再头疼。</span></p>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"200\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-top: 30px;\" width=\"30\" data-imgfileid=\"100037607\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e2c7085&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fym794MIAO6XZRMe0SVBmiau2q0s5wlicHeUiaGRqm2xPSvhne9gZrv5lQNXpxEMpkfT3FaiaR8JUVx3HKHCvTLfxhol16b23Po53pXM3QJwCnqk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   <h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;color: black;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-top: 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">💎 样式体系重构</span></h1>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">v5 的样式基于 Less，这在早期是明智的选择，但 Less 的维护活跃度持续下降。v6 全面迁移到现代 CSS 方案：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;color: black;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">Tailwind CSS v4</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：原子化 CSS，布局和间距不再需要写自定义样式</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">antd-style v4</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：消费 antd Design Token 的 CSS-in-JS 方案，主题切换零成本</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">CSS Modules</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：组件级样式隔离，避免命名冲突</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时启用 antd CSS 变量模式（cssVar），不仅支持动态主题切换，渲染性能也有提升。</span></p>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"200\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-top: 30px;\" width=\"30\" data-imgfileid=\"100037604\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dba93bda&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fym794MIAO6WuohcRiaDL7VlVzpKqicibFiaag52yg5b2fSgdwc19P2TroSn1wDk04fKa405taT6d40XicVdxxVhqdRdGxICAicOBcIibd6EWQQftyY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   <h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;color: black;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-top: 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">⚡ 构建提速</span></h1>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">v5 使用 mfsu（基于 webpack 5）做依赖预编译，v6 切换到&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">utoopack</span></span><sup style=\"line-height: 0;color: #1e6bb8;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">[5]</span></sup><span leaf=\"\">（Turbopack + Rust 核心），构建速度显著提升：</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n    <table style=\"display: table;text-align: left;\">\n     <thead>\n      <tr style=\"border: 0;border-top: 1px solid #ccc;background-color: white;\">\n       <th style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;background-color: #fff;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">版本</span></p>\n       </th>\n       <th style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;background-color: #fff;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">构建工具</span></p>\n       </th>\n       <th style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;background-color: #fff;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">生产构建耗时</span></p>\n       </th>\n      </tr>\n     </thead>\n     <tbody>\n      <tr style=\"border: 0;border-top: 1px solid #ccc;background-color: white;\">\n       <td style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">v5.2.0</span></p>\n       </td>\n       <td style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">webpack 5 (mfsu)</span></p>\n       </td>\n       <td style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">~15.5s</span></p>\n       </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border: 0;border-top: 1px solid #ccc;background-color: #fff;\">\n       <td style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">v6.0.0</span></p>\n       </td>\n       <td style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">utoopack (Turbopack)</span></p>\n       </td>\n       <td style=\"font-size: 16px;border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px 10px;text-align: left;min-width: 85px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">~9.0s</span></p>\n       </td>\n      </tr>\n     </tbody>\n    </table>\n   </p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border: none;display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);color: #6a737d;padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 20px;padding-right: 10px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-top: 20px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0px;color: black;line-height: 26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">测试环境：Apple M-series, Node 22</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">生产构建提速约&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">42%</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，日常开发中冷启动和 HMR 提升更为明显。同时启用了&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;color: #1e6bb8;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">routePrefetch</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;路由预加载，页面切换更加流畅。</span></p>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"200\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-top: 30px;\" width=\"30\" data-imgfileid=\"100037608\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=62127144&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fym794MIAO6UQ0nSkRydTp42EEHtjNWd6R4ewLYW9I2PrpTRzLtEoYrAuN5NKVnpAL6C74mOO5rx0uxUciaicJ1m0ibdSyUTibyic6bQ9XcodwcBo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   <h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;color: black;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-top: 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🤖 AI 能力</span></h1>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;line-height: 26px;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">v6 新增了 AI 助手页面，基于 Ant Design X 构建。这是一个开箱即用的聊天界面示例，展示了如何在 Pro 项目中集成 AI 对话能力。</span></p>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"200\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-top: 30px;\" width=\"30\" data-imgfileid=\"100037611\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6ca17484&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fym794MIAO6Vsl3l1azQFEviaqO7YzWAo5ggteoz0lCQia8ZsHicbxjQnZxPmtfveK4E7jcVPXQ9xjqnWz5Tiaib7FUE3pqKZMwxfeWjVhJhrhiaJM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   <h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;padding: 0px;color: black;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-top: 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔧 工具链现代化</span></h1>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;color: black;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">Biome</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;替代 ESLint + Prettier — 一个工具搞定 lint + format，速度快 10 倍以上，告别多个配置文件的繁琐</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;color: rgb(1,1,1);font-weight: 500;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span leaf=\"\">React Query</span><